    <HediffDef ParentName="CNHediffOther">
        <defName>CNHyperClotBloodReplacement</defName>
        <label>HyperClot Blood Replacement</label>
        <labelNoun>HyperClot Blood Replacement</labelNoun>
		<description>HyperClot is a full blood replacement that utilizes remote infrastructure to function. HyperClot contains artifical platelets that form a meshnet with other platelets in the bloodstream. When a bleeding injury is detected, the artificial platelets are coordinated to close the wound quickly.\n\nLike all full blood replacements, HyperClot enhances the ability of the body to move oxygen around.</description>
